            <fr:taxon>Lemma</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="jms-0023.xml" title="Positively generated dcpos" addr="jms-0023" type="local">positively generated</fr:link> <fr:link href="jms-001S.xml" title="Pointed dcpo" addr="jms-001S" type="local">pointed</fr:link> dcpo. Then <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> has an <fr:link href="jms-0022.xml" title="Open positivity predicate" addr="jms-0022" type="local">open positivity predicate</fr:link>.</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="tomdejong.xml" title="Tom de Jong" addr="tomdejong" type="local">Tom de Jong</fr:link></fr:author><fr:author><fr:link href="martinescardo.xml" title="Martín Hötzel Escardó" addr="martinescardo" type="local">Martín Hötzel Escardó</fr:link></fr:author><fr:author><fr:link href="jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>2</fr:month><fr:day>16</fr:day></fr:date><fr:anchor>7048</fr:anchor><fr:addr type="machine">unstable/2467</fr:addr><fr:route>unstable-2467.xml</fr:route><fr:title text="" /><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
  <fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[I\subseteq  A]]></fr:tex> be a directed subset such that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\bigsqcup {I}]]></fr:tex> is positive; we must find a positive element of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[I]]></fr:tex>. Because <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="jms-0023.xml" title="Positively generated dcpos" addr="jms-0023" type="local">positively generated</fr:link> we know that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\bigsqcup {I} \sqsubseteq  \bigsqcup {\mathopen {}\left (I\cap  A^+\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>. Because <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\bigsqcup {I}]]></fr:tex> is positive and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[I\cap  A^+]]></fr:tex> <fr:link href="jms-0028.xml" title="The positive part of a semidirected subset is semidirected" addr="jms-0028" type="local">is semidirected</fr:link>, it follows that the latter is inhabited.</fr:p>
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
</fr:mainmatter>
